rows.label: campfev11_140_175_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, Satahiko! We'll be heading out to
Gula pretty soon. Taking the
ferry from Yanchik.

rows.label: campfev11_140_175_msg0003
rows.name: Have you ever been to Gula?

rows.label: campfev11_140_175_msg0005
rows.name:
How about a Divine Beast ship? Been on one
of those before?

rows.label: campfev11_140_175_msg0008
rows.name:
Well, you might a get a bit sick.
But you won't get bored! First time
on a boat's loads of fun!

rows.label: campfev11_140_175_msg0009
rows.name: We're gonna have a blast Sata!
